claim.claim-text:
A refrigerator, comprising:
a body;
a freezing compartment formed inside the body;
a refrigerating compartment formed inside the body;
a freezing compartment door rotatably connected to the body for closing the freezing compartment;
a refrigerating compartment door rotatably connected to the body for closing the refrigerating compartment; and
an ice making compartment formed between the freezing compartment and the refrigerating compartment inside the body and accessible without opening either of the freezing compartment and the refrigerating compartment doors.
